Description: Jinja2 ``os.path`` Filters
        ==========================
        
        A Jinja2 extension that introduces the template filters ``basename`` and
        ``dirname``.
        
        Examples
        --------
        
        .. code:: python
        
            my_path = "/some/absolute/path/with/file.txt"
            {{ my_path | basename }}
        
        Will fill in ``'file.txt'``.
        
        .. code:: python
        
            my_path = "/some/absolute/path/with/file.txt"
            {{ my_path | dirname }}
        
        Will fill in ``'/some/absolute/path/with'``.
        
